high_descs: Walk straight and head towards the stool on your left.
Grab the cup on the counter.
Turn left and head towards the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the cup to the left of the lettuce, close the fridge for the cup to cool down, and take out the cup.
Turn right towards the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Placed the cooled cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk forward until the black stools are even with you then turn left to face them.
Pick up the mug to the left of the butter knife.
Turn left and walk to the fridge so you are standing in front of it facing it.
Chill the mug in the fridge then retrieve it and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the coffee maker to the left of the sink.
Place the mug in it's spot under the coffee maker's spout.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: walk straight to the two stools
grab the cup on the counter
turn left, walk to the refrigerator on the left
open the refrigerator, put the cup in, wait a while, take the cup out
turn right, walk to the coffee machine
put the cup down in the coffee machine
anns.task_desc: cool the cup in the refrigerator, put it in the coffee machine

high_descs: Walk across the room and turn right facing the bar
Pick up the coffee mug that's on the bar
Turn left and head across the room then hang right and head to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and place the mug on the second shelf then close the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and pick up the mug on the second shelf then close the refrigerator
Turn around and head to the coffee maker on your left and place mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place coffee mug in a coffee maker
